nal issue, while concerning, is less likely to impair flight safety than the lack of calmness or reliability seen in the other candidates.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fB\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
