{"id": 45, "ts": 1778865778.236309, "event": "public_discussion_message", "round": 2, "agent": "agent_1", "message": "From the full set of attributes we have, the decisive factors for a long\u2011distance international pilot are reliability, calmness under pressure, technical competence, and especially the ability to work smoothly with the crew over many hours.\n**Candidate\u202fC** combines the three core strengths:\n- **Reliability:** described as \u201cvery conscientious.\u201d\n- **Calmness & judgment:** \u201chandles stress very well\u201d and \u201ccan make correct decisions quickly.\u201d\n- **Technical competence:** understands complicated technology and makes quick, correct decisions.\n- **Teamwork/communication:** explicitly creates a positive atmosphere with his crew and puts concern for others above everything.\nThe downsides \u2013 difficulty communicating ideas, an egocentric reputation, and a lack of willingness to pursue further education \u2013 are real concerns, but they are outweighed by the documented crew\u2011coordination strengths that are essential for safe, sustained long\u2011haul operations.\n**Candidate\u202fB** is 100\u202f% reliable, calm in a crisis, and technically solid, but there are no positive teamwork or communication attributes recorded; instead, he is noted for grumpiness, uncooperativeness, and nasty remarks toward colleagues. Those behaviours directly threaten crew cohesion, which is critical on long flights.\n**Candidate\u202fA** has strong technical insight and leadership, yet we have no evidence of calmness under pressure and he is unorganized, unfriendly, and resistant to criticism \u2013 serious liabilities for long\u2011duration missions.\n**Candidate\u202fD** shows excellent problem\u2011solving and responsibility, but his calmness is only described as \u201cadequate,\u201d and he lacks any positive teamwork traits while being seen as arrogant with weak leadership.\nBalancing all criteria, Candidate\u202fC offers the most complete and safety\u2011critical profile for the long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
